{"tid":166551,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［你問佢地答系列］魔術師/氣球師/花式跳繩港隊","createTime":"2017-03-22T07:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T06:18:15.000Z","uid":74954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c627b4a62e47f39a7fdb1086bd476d7e9bf2571","tid":166551,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"大家盡情發問，我地遲d會邀請幾個不同既以興趣為專業既人士去做專訪 ，講下佢地行業/外人既誤解。<br />\n而第一波簡左魔術師/氣球師同花式跳繩<br />\n<br />\n咁我地希望好玩d <br />\n而家有個答問環節希望開放俾大家發問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家既問題重復得越多 就會優先問/一定問<br />\n<br />\n問咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以問d尖銳&amp;#21874;&amp;#22021;問題<br />\n可以一次問哂3個人<br />\n每人最多問3個問題<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n同埋佢地會分別係條片教大家一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會想佢地教你咩<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------<br />\n預計條片會係15/4出街<br />\n到時再通知大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比小小background <br />\n<br />\n魔術師：<br />\n佢入行都十幾年<br />\n但仲係無女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n單身<br />\n係業界都受人尊重<br />\n算搵到食<br />\n鐘意玩玩具<br />\n任問<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n氣球師：<br />\n已婚<br />\n入行都十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無其他資料，任問<br />\n<br />\n花式跳繩港隊：<br />\n任問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36859287d0ab2a665d8bd693059697ea8439192","tid":166551,"uid":26399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T07:53:05.000Z","msg":"魔術師唔會係Louis掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c39f9cfa7ad9314ce3985408bac9bf29af8cef","tid":166551,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魔術師唔會係Louis掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/no